        <updateDate>2021-04-26T14:21:56Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Help Independent Tracks Succeed Act or the HITS Act</b></p> <p>This bill permits taxpayers to treat as currently deductible expenses the cost of qualified sound recording productions not exceeding $150,000 in a taxable year. The bill defines <i>qualified sound recording production</i> as certain sound recordings produced and recorded in the United States. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
